  "remarks": "\nHabibollah SAYYARI is an involved person within the meaning of the Iran (Sanctions) Regulations 2023 as through his roles as Head of the Joint Staff of the Iranian Army and is Deputy Chief of the Iranian Army for Coordination, SAYYARI is or has been involved in hostile activity by the Government of Iran, namely threatening, planning or conducting activity which is intended to undermine the integrity, prosperity or security of Israel.\n",
